'''日本札幌圣殿'''（{{lang-ja|日本札幌神殿}}）是[[耶稣基督后期圣徒教会|耶稣基督后期圣徒教会]]第151个开放的圣殿，位于日本[[札幌市|札幌市]][[厚别区|厚别区]]大谷地西1丁目6-1，是继[[日本东京圣殿|日本东京圣殿]]和[[日本福冈圣殿|日本福冈圣殿]]之后日本的第三座圣殿. 2009年10月3日，耶稣基督后期圣徒教会宣布在札幌修建圣殿<ref>{{citation |url= http://www.deseretnews.com/article/705334251/Brigham-City-among-five-new-locales-for-LDS-temples.html |title= Brigham City among five new locales for LDS temples |first= Scott |last= Taylor |date= October 4, 2009 |newspaper= Deseret News |access-date= 2012-11-06 |archive-date= 2018-07-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180730105032/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/705334251/Brigham-City-among-five-new-locales-for-LDS-temples.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2016年8月21日，Russel M. Nelson 会长主持奉献仪式<ref name="dedication-sapporo">{{citation |url= https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/article/sapporo-japan-temple-dedicated |title= Sapporo Japan Temple Dedicated in Three Sessions: Third Mormon temple in Japan, 151st operating temple worldwide |work= Newsroom |publisher= [[LDS_Church|LDS Church]] |date= 2016-08-21 |accessdate= 2021-01-19 |archive-date= 2021-01-28 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210128004758/https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/article/sapporo-japan-temple-dedicated |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

